                <h5>Current System: Sol</h5>
                <p>Primary purpose will be for support at home, BGS, and black market trading.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="carrier">
                <h3>IHCF FREEDOM FLAGSHIP</h3>
                <h5>Current System: Lajit</h5>
                <p>Primary purpose will be for support at home, BGS, and bounty hunting carrier missions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="carrier">
                <h3>IHCF MINERS RESPITE</h3>
                <h5>Current System: HIP 64714</h5>
                <p>Primary purpose will be for support at home, long range mining, commodity trading.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="carrier">
                <h3>IHCF VINDICATOR</h3>
                <h5>Current System: Mariphobo</h5>
                <p>Primary purpose will be for support at home, BGS, and black market trading.</p>
            </div>
